"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**熱敏感物質是否存在?**\\n\\n**這詞彙大多使用於醫學上，泛指因人體皮膚在遇到溫度變化時，使皮膚產生紅疹，發癢等皮膚病症，又稱\\\\[慢性蕁麻疹\\\\]。**\\n\\n但是除了人體會因溫度變化，產生熱敏感的現象之外。\\n\\n其他動物是否也會有類似的病症呢？\\n\\n甚至，如果把溫度變化帶來的影響，除動物以外，再更進一步研究到植物圈。\\n\\n那麼對植物來說，是否也會產生熱敏感的症狀?\\n\\n植物體內是否含有\\\\[熱敏感物質\\\\]?\\n\\n如果植物體內的熱敏感物質存在，那麼，觸發熱敏感的溫度會是在哪個臨界點呢？\\n\\n在探討\\\\[低溫乾燥\\\\]的產業時，首先得面對的議題，便是\\\\[熱敏感物質是否存在於植物體內?\\\\]的提問。\\n\\n然後才能更進一步的，針對不同植物的生物特性去研究熱敏感物質所帶來的影響與變化。\\n\\n<Are heat sensitive substances present?>\\n\\nThis term is mostly used in medicine. It generally refers to skin conditions such as rashes and itching when the human skin encounters temperature changes. It is also known as \\\\[chronic urticaria\\\\].\\n\\nBut except for the phenomenon that the human body is sensitive to heat due to temperature changes.\\n\\nWill other animals have similar symptoms?\\n\\nEven if the effects of temperature changes are considered, in addition to animals, we can further study the plant circle.\\n\\nSo for plants, does it also produce symptoms of heat sensitivity?\\n\\nDo plants contain \\\\[heat sensitive substances\\\\]?\\n\\nIf there are heat-sensitive substances in plants, then, at which critical point will the temperature that trigger heat sensitivity be?\\n\\nWhen discussing the industry of \\\\[low temperature drying\\\\], the first issue we have to face is the question of \\\\[Does heat-sensitive substances exist in plants?\\\\].\\n\\nOnly then can we go one step further and study the effects and changes brought about by heat-sensitive substances according to the biological characteristics of different plants.\\n\\n** \\n **\",\"timestamp\":1640915980,\"title\":\"熱敏感物質是否存在?Are heat sensitive substances present?\"},\"digest\":\"P3QG2UAUNRi4Pyi7sOFU3EwH1djoaRz26d518MuU4MA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xef9d81473Ea7E87cFc707346B204Cb31cCEEDB1B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"u-3KuTkoDDIwvDuFVKjR3Qff_xtuoBy2U9ObtcqcqCc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hZ01KzGe-MCVXVtPdNPIZbbkegUqv6mxu5uP_BHFWEU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"htmcgiQa7pvawFRkHQtlUwd-1LzrBpk_-LMVjHmHY986vsCv9S8QObJfq0jZ1DU2-43O1wHG0VX2SyPtSlQQIw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd2a4cc9f239fedb45fb45f49372a3b797d5a1c9c669258a48b134707b2232ffe73a556e5223d7c462c88b92c845daccc2410dc0f40fe1978cb2b4bdb3fd119241c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"u-3KuTkoDDIwvDuFVKjR3Qff_xtuoBy2U9ObtcqcqCc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hZ01KzGe-MCVXVtPdNPIZbbkegUqv6mxu5uP_BHFWEU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"P3QG2UAUNRi4Pyi7sOFU3EwH1djoaRz26d518MuU4MA\"}"